          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0347P0-05169'>
        <a name='S6CV0347P0_20000406_WH_41'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-gisela-stuart' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0347P0_20000406_WH_41' title='Link to this speech by Ms Gisela Stuart' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
