            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_276wh' title='Col. 276WH &mdash; HC Deb 06 April 2000 vol 347 c276WH' name='column_276wh' href='#column_276wh' rel='bookmark'>276WH</a>
            their research. Hon. Members should accept that the evaluation is independent, and that we have not even thought about political convenience. We want genuinely independent research. That is why&#x2014;
          </p>
